{"tid":1535394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於欺凌幼犬。我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:24:25.000Z","uid":295735,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"96c249b9396d0c271b2a393d67299b062bdb8d4c","tid":1535394,"uid":295735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:46:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！你地咪撚錯重點呀！ <br />\n依家係班犬！同佢地既藍朋友聯手用佢地既特權欺凌我地啲兄弟姐妹呀！  唔撚係我地欺凌佢地呀！ <br />\n我地只係還拖咋！<br />\n所以。兄弟姊妹放膽做！ <br />\n<br />\n#不分化 #不割蓆"},{"pid":"fe89e2815778fca17adae29cff59096755f93afc","tid":1535394,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:46:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d3f0829a9be59fefe5897e4546aba5a5f8caf36","tid":1535394,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:47:04.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1d0ea92d37c2f7058da5f7c54371b3